name: Jeetjail
description: JeetJail is a community-driven meme project on Solana built to transform the culture of early selling and market panic in crypto. The project promotes strong conviction, unity, and long-term thinking by rewarding holders and fostering a humorous yet disciplined “no-jeet” mentality. Through its viral identity, strong community engagement, and transparent launch, JeetJail aims to create a sustainable, fun, and educational movement where conviction meets culture.
